name: TestBuddy
text: That's not how I inteeded for things to work out.

name: TestBuddy
text: But you can't beat all the basement dwellers in one go.

name: TestBuddy
text: And now that you're in this basement.

name: TestBuddy
text: I hope you're ready, because this next guy.

text: Was trained by THEE Dunkey himself.

name: TestBuddy
text: I'll be seeing you soon enough, chump.
